程序包 syntaxtree

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Node
    The interface which all syntax tree classes must implement.
    NodeListInterface
    The interface which NodeList, NodeListOptional, and NodeSequence implement.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ALoadStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "ALOAD" f1 -> Reg() f2 -> SpilledArg()
    AStoreStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "ASTORE" f1 -> SpilledArg() f2 -> Reg()
    BinOp
    Grammar production: f0 -> Operator() f1 -> Reg() f2 -> SimpleExp()
    CallStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "CALL" f1 -> SimpleExp()
    CJumpStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "CJUMP" f1 -> Reg() f2 -> Label()
    ErrorStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "ERROR"
    Exp
    Grammar production: f0 -> HAllocate() | BinOp() | SimpleExp()
    Goal
    Grammar production: f0 -> "MAIN" f1 -> "[" f2 -> IntegerLiteral() f3 -> "]" f4 -> "[" f5 -> IntegerLiteral() f6 -> "]" f7 -> "[" f8 -> IntegerLiteral() f9 -> "]" f10 -> StmtList() f11 -> "END" f12 -> ( Procedure() )* f13 ->
    HAllocate
    Grammar production: f0 -> "HALLOCATE" f1 -> SimpleExp()
    HLoadStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "HLOAD" f1 -> Reg() f2 -> Reg() f3 -> IntegerLiteral()
    HStoreStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "HSTORE" f1 -> Reg() f2 -> IntegerLiteral() f3 -> Reg()
    IntegerLiteral
    Grammar production: f0 ->
    JumpStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "JUMP" f1 -> Label()
    Label
    Grammar production: f0 ->
    MoveStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "MOVE" f1 -> Reg() f2 -> Exp()
    NodeChoice
    Represents a grammar choice, e.g. ( A | B )
    NodeList
    Represents a grammar list, e.g. ( A )+
    NodeListOptional
    Represents an optional grammar list, e.g. ( A )*
    NodeOptional
    Represents an grammar optional node, e.g. ( A )?
    NodeSequence
    Represents a sequence of nodes nested within a choice, list, optional list, or optional, e.g. ( A B )+ or [ C D E ]
    NodeToken
    Represents a single token in the grammar.
    NoOpStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "NOOP"
    Operator
    Grammar production: f0 -> "LT" | "PLUS" | "MINUS" | "TIMES"
    PassArgStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "PASSARG" f1 -> IntegerLiteral() f2 -> Reg()
    PrintStmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> "PRINT" f1 -> SimpleExp()
    Procedure
    Grammar production: f0 -> Label() f1 -> "[" f2 -> IntegerLiteral() f3 -> "]" f4 -> "[" f5 -> IntegerLiteral() f6 -> "]" f7 -> "[" f8 -> IntegerLiteral() f9 -> "]" f10 -> StmtList() f11 -> "END"
    Reg
    Grammar production: f0 -> "a0" | "a1" | "a2" | "a3" | "t0" | "t1" | "t2" | "t3" | "t4" | "t5" | "t6" | "t7" | "s0" | "s1" | "s2" | "s3" | "s4" | "s5" | "s6" | "s7" | "t8" | "t9" | "v0" | "v1"
    SimpleExp
    Grammar production: f0 -> Reg() | IntegerLiteral() | Label()
    SpilledArg
    Grammar production: f0 -> "SPILLEDARG" f1 -> IntegerLiteral()
    Stmt
    Grammar production: f0 -> NoOpStmt() | ErrorStmt() | CJumpStmt() | JumpStmt() | HStoreStmt() | HLoadStmt() | MoveStmt() | PrintStmt() | ALoadStmt() | AStoreStmt() | PassArgStmt() | CallStmt()
    StmtList
    Grammar production: f0 -> ( ( Label() )?
